name: Cheesed out Anime Backgrounds
description:
Cheesed out Anime Backgrounds

Please note: GENERATION SERVICES please ask, because this has another model mixed in, and it may not be kind to yoink this AS WELL AS not asking the cheese master first.

A quiet mix of

  • Anime Backgrounds (Trained model) https://civitai.com/models/6417/anime-backgrounds

  • Cheesedaddy's Landscape Mix (i'm not sure which version so i'm linking both) - (OG) https://civitai.com/models/5041/cheese-daddys-landscapes-mix (OFFSET NOISE) https://civitai.com/models/15037/cheese-daddys-landscapes-mix-or-offset-noise by cheesedaddy

  • Wave Concepts (byus) https://civitai.com/models/7488/wave-concepts-backgrounds (This is in v 1.2 not 1.0)

There ARE other mixes to come but i'd like to test them before adding the versions here.

VAE Is optional, as I don't remember which one we consistently used.

LYCORIS EXTRACTION IS HERE FOR 1.2: https://civitai.com/models/30574?modelVersionId=36862 Thank KAPPA THE EXTRACTION MASTER!!!
